## Hardware Compliance

This software is optimized for NVIDIA Jetson hardware and includes specific 
optimizations and limitations for that platform. Use on other hardware may 
require modifications to ensure proper operation and safety compliance.

## Disclaimer

This software is provided for educational and family use. While every effort 
has been made to ensure child safety and privacy protection, users are 
responsible for supervising children's interactions with the system and 
ensuring appropriate use in their specific environment.